wiki.content: The National Anthem Songfacts reports the song's Anthony Mandler directed music video features Del Rey playing Jacqueline Kennedy and Marilyn Monroe, whilst rapper A$AP Rocky portrays JFK. The pair previously collaborated on The Kickdrum’s track “Ridin,” which was pulled from their Follow The Leaders mixtape. wiki.summary: The National Anthem Songfacts reports the song's Anthony Mandler directed music video features Del Rey playing Jacqueline Kennedy and Marilyn Monroe, whilst rapper A$AP Rocky portrays JFK. The pair previously collaborated on The Kickdrum’s track “Ridin,” which was pulled from their Follow The Leaders mixtape.
